transcript:
Agent: Hi, is this Mr. Johnson?
Customer: Yes, it is. Who's calling?
Agent: My name is Emily, and I'm calling from GreenTech Solutions. We specialize in energy-efficient lighting systems.
Customer: Okay, I've heard of you. What can you do for me?
Agent: We've recently launched a new line of LED bulbs that can help reduce your energy consumption by up to 50%.
Customer: That sounds interesting. I've been looking to cut down my electricity bill.
Agent: Exactly! Our bulbs are not only energy-efficient but also have a longer lifespan compared to traditional bulbs.
Customer: How much do they cost?
Agent: Our starter package begins at $50, which includes 5 bulbs and a 5-year warranty.
Customer: That's a bit pricey. What kind of savings can I expect?
Agent: Based on average usage, you can expect to save around $10-15 per month.
Customer: Okay, that's a good point. Can you send me some more information?
Agent: Absolutely, I can email you a brochure and some case studies.
Customer: That would be great, thank you.
Agent: You're welcome, Mr. Johnson. I'll send that over right away.
Customer: Thanks, Emily. I look forward to reviewing the information.
Agent: Great, and if you have any questions or would like to place an order, just give me a call.
Customer: Will do, thanks again.
Agent: You're welcome, have a great day!
